{
  "_readme": [
    "Copy file ini ke settings.local.json (tanpa .example) dan sesuaikan dengan OS/setup kamu.",
    "File ini git-tracked (aman di-commit). settings.local.json adalah git-ignored.",
    "Atau jalankan: /init-project --local-only  → Claude akan auto-detect OS dan generate settings.local.json.",
    "Pilih salah satu blok OS di bawah, hapus sisanya, rename key ke 'permissions'."
  ],

  "_security_notes": [
    "JANGAN gunakan wildcard runtime: Bash(python3 *), Bash(node *), Bash(npm *), Bash(bun *)",
    "  → Wildcard tsb = arbitrary code execution",
    "GUNAKAN scope sempit: Bash(python3 ./**/*.py) = hanya file .py di project dir",
    "SELALU sertakan deny block: rm -rf dan sudo minimal"
  ],

  "permissions_WINDOWS": {
    "allow": [
      "Read(./**)",
      "Read(~/.claude/**)",
      "Read({{PROJECT_ROOT}}/**)",
      "Bash(git *)",
      "Bash(php *)",
      "Bash(mysql *)",
      "Bash(composer *)",
      "Bash(powershell -ExecutionPolicy Bypass -File *)",
      "Bash(bash -n ~/.claude/scripts/statusline.sh)",
      "Bash(chmod -R u+w .git/)",
      "Skill(update-config)",
      "Grep(**)",
      "Glob(**)",
      "Monitor(**)",
      "Write(./experiments/**)",
      "Write(./.claude/**)",
      "Edit(./.claude/**)",
      "Write({{PROJECT_ROOT}}/**)",
      "Edit({{PROJECT_ROOT}}/**)"
    ],
    "deny": [
      "Bash(rm -rf *)",
      "Bash(sudo *)"
    ],
    "additionalDirectories": [
      "~/.claude",
      "{{PROJECT_ROOT}}"
    ]
  },

